libsndfile:  libsndfile (A C library for reading/writing sounds)
libsndfile: It is multi-platform, and can handle little and big-endian files.
libsndfile: 
libsndfile: It's features:
libsndfile:   Read and write many WAV file formats.
libsndfile:   Simple, elegant and easy API
libsndfile:   On the fly conversion      
libsndfile:   Optional normalization
